\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5850145 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7222697\charrsid14627296 It's just showing that it is not as important as it once was.
